exceptions.tactic: destruct (list_app_eq_inv X l1 l2 r1 (x :: r2) H) as [left | right].
exceptions.exn: In environment X : Type l1, l2, r1, r2 : list X x : X H : l1 ++ r1 = l2 ++ x :: r2 The term "X" has type "Type" while it is expected to have type "list ?X".

original: intros H. destruct (list_app_eq_inv X l1 l2 r1 (x :: r2) H) as [left | right]. - left. destruct left as [m [H1 H2]]. exists m. split. + auto. + auto. - right. destruct right as [m [H1 H2]]. exists m. split. + auto. + apply app_inv_tail in H2. auto.
